{"tid":232470,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[凌晨消息]2016-17 LIHKG香港超級女神聯賽煞科 朱千雪問鼎首屆冠軍","createTime":"2017-05-06T18:11:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-07T13:26:55.000Z","uid":92376,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e4b1cbec110f70415f3b5594b33c3db7a666fa57","tid":232470,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T18:11:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/17WV586.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F17WV586.png&h=e48927db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n完整積分榜<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/9uJZisl.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9uJZisl.png&h=6f3f8338&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冠軍:<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/8CQUpUM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F8CQUpUM.png&h=a452de4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱千雪（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n亞軍:<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/KztEFtl.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKztEFtl.png&h=596fc166&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李佳芯（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n季軍:<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/CARupl2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FCARupl2.png&h=67b94b3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n謝安琪（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n來季環球女神冠軍盃分組賽資格<br />\n朱千雪(第1種子)<br />\n李佳芯、謝安琪(第2種子)<br />\n<br />\n來季環球女神冠軍盃分組賽附加賽資格<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/NRYaLqj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNRYaLqj.png&h=1fb0cdd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳穎欣@SG（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n降班至2017-18 LIHKG香港冠軍女神聯賽<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/dyvWvIn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FdyvWvIn.png&h=905c20d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n莊錠欣（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Nr0V19R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNr0V19R.png&h=28b169dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n袁澧林（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n0分勒令退聯失去來季參賽資格:<br />\n岑晉晴<br />\n<br />\n無論你係欣賞又好唔欣賞呢次賽事都好,今季超級聯賽已經塵埃落定啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本季餘下冠甲乙三組常規聯賽及升班附加賽希望大家會支持落去<br />\n我地下季超級聯賽再見,到時會有更多新鮮驚喜,休季期間都會有新鮮企劃,等住大家黎參與架,呢道投選大門係一直為大家打開架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"362202891b1992e9d60c381a596c3fb100ece889","tid":232470,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T18:22:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/8jnwIJ8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F8jnwIJ8.png&h=2bdbbb93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n修訂版積分榜(更新岑晉晴出局概要)"},{"pid":"de679dda5d60b37a6c40839519ba3b402ef0cbda","tid":232470,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T19:27:18.000Z","msg":"朱千雪張圖可唔可以執下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幫你send埋去蘋果日報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e897b766ecc7f7eaebeb7b3dd20ac30d83a8b93","tid":232470,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:01:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>朱千雪張圖可唔可以執下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幫你send埋去蘋果日報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點執法?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f0ffee83f3736236e56593ba12a850ab5af4be","tid":232470,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:34:54.000Z","